data.Sentence_cn: 几乎过了一个星期，那姑娘才能讲述自己的遭遇。
data.Sentence: Nearly a week passed before the girl was able to explain what had happened to her.

data.Sentence_cn: 一天下午，她乘小船从海岸出发，遇上了风暴。
data.Sentence: One afternoon she set out from the coast in a small boat and was caught in a storm.

data.Sentence_cn: 天将黑时，小船撞在了一块礁石上，姑娘跳进了海里。
data.Sentence: Towards evening, the boat struck a rock and the girl jumped into the sea.

data.Sentence_cn: 她在海里游了整整一夜才游到岸边。
data.Sentence: Then she swam to the shore after spending the whole night in the water.

data.Sentence_cn: 在那段时间里，她游了8英里。
data.Sentence: During that time she covered a distance of eight miles.

data.Sentence_cn: 第二天凌晨，她看到前方有灯光，
data.Sentence: Early next morning, she saw a light ahead.

data.Sentence_cn: 知道自己已经接近岸边了，因为那灯光是在高高的峭壁上。
data.Sentence: She knew she was near the shore because the light was high up on the cliffs.

data.Sentence_cn: 到达岸边后，姑娘朝着她看到的灯光方向挣扎着往峭壁上爬去。
data.Sentence: On arriving at the shore, the girl struggled up the cliff towards the light she had seen.

data.Sentence_cn: 第二天她醒来时，发现自己躺在医院里。
data.Sentence: When she woke up a day later, she found herself in hospital.
